  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Public Action for Resilience (PAR) Activity</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to support local communities to strengthen resilience to possible violent extremist influences and radicalization. The proposed project has a strong empowerment component and includes capacity building for relevant local actors in order to increase knowledge and understanding of radicalization as a process undermining social cohesion, its drivers, and ways of enhancing local resilience to it.</narrative>
  </description>
